{"tid":1149694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"喺屋企同四件廢老傾香港政治環境","createTime":"2019-05-11T10:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T12:54:39.000Z","uid":144312,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cbf42f0e20d6bad4a64c2bf69e652b93e56ab579","tid":1149694,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:25:11.000Z","msg":"佢地四個輪流轟炸我咁，痴孖筋。我屋企兩老都算，我不嬲知佢地咩料。點知原來個Uncle同Auntie都一撚樣，一齊屌鳩建制派班人渣，好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四件加埋都二百幾歲，全部都頭腦好清晰，知道共產黨有幾撚衰，知道香港而加嘅政治環境有幾惡劣，知道而加香港嘅法治程度有幾差。<br />\n<br />\n好慶幸岀生喺呢個屋企，可以教導到我正確嘅價值觀，令我識得分是非黑白，會同我分析香港嘅大環境。<br />\n<br />\n不過我知唔係個個家庭都好似我咁好彩，希望屋企有真廢老嘅人，要教導翻啲廢老我相信就唔係咁容易喇，但都要保持自己清晰嘅頭腦，香港加油"},{"pid":"a1ec3777cbd85cf20d02589a282a58d206ae8cbd","tid":1149694,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:26:42.000Z","msg":"我全個家族都係廢老得我係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316de895028772267997a7c3601c669ebbb0546b","tid":1149694,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1ec3777cbd85cf20d02589a282a58d206ae8cbd","tid":1149694,"uid":165336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T10:26:42.000Z","msg":"我全個家族都係廢老得我係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:01:00.000Z","msg":"出淤泥而不染都唔容易"},{"pid":"25454606e0a698feff596295053515f0bbcc62ef","tid":1149694,"uid":67346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n四老知理仲要罵埋佢地廢老"},{"pid":"39e05186ddb5c6380c17b172b27ecfccb2f02492","tid":1149694,"uid":144312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25454606e0a698feff596295053515f0bbcc62ef","tid":1149694,"uid":67346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <